## DTO Patterns

### Basic DTO with Built Value

```dart
// features/auth/data/models/user_dto.dart
abstract class UserDto implements Built<UserDto, UserDtoBuilder> {
  static Serializer<UserDto> get serializer => _$userDtoSerializer;

  String get id;
  String get name;
  String? get email;

  UserDto._();
  factory UserDto([void Function(UserDtoBuilder) updates]) = _$UserDto;

  // Convert to domain model
  User toDomain() => User(id: id, name: name, email: email);
}
```

### Response DTO with Nested Data

```dart
abstract class UserResponseDto
    implements Built<UserResponseDto, UserResponseDtoBuilder> {
  static Serializer<UserResponseDto> get serializer =>
      _$userResponseDtoSerializer;

  UserDto get data;
  String? get message;

  UserResponseDto._();
  factory UserResponseDto([void Function(UserResponseDtoBuilder) updates]) =
      _$UserResponseDto;
}
```

