## Serializers Registration

All enums and DTOs must be registered in `core/api/serializers.dart`:

```dart
@SerializersFor([
  // DTOs
  UserDto,
  LoginRequestDto,
  LoginResponseDto,
  DashboardResponseDto,
  NotificationDto,
  PaginationMetaDto,
  // Enums
  NotificationReadFilter,
  BooleanFlag,
  DashboardStatsType,
  ApplicationType,
  ApplicationStatus,
])
final Serializers serializers =
    (_$serializers.toBuilder()
          ..addPlugin(IntToBoolPlugin())      // Converts int 0/1 to bool
          ..addPlugin(StringToNumberPlugin()) // Converts string numbers
          ..addPlugin(StandardJsonPlugin()))
        .build();
```

### Custom Serializer Plugins

Located in `core/api/serializers/`:

| Plugin | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `IntToBoolPlugin` | Converts API `0`/`1` integers to `bool` |
| `StringToNumberPlugin` | Converts string numbers to `int`/`double` |
| `StandardJsonPlugin` | Standard JSON serialization |

