## API Client Configuration

Located in `core/api/api_client.dart`:

```dart
class ApiClient {
  static ChopperClient create({String? baseUrl, String? token}) {
    return ChopperClient(
      baseUrl: Uri.parse(baseUrl ?? ApiConfig.baseUrl),
      services: [
        AuthService.create(),
        NotificationService.create(),
        // Add all services
      ],
      converter: BuiltValueConverter(),
      interceptors: [
        HeaderInterceptor(),
        if (token != null) AuthInterceptor(token),
        HttpLoggingInterceptor(),
      ],
    );
  }
}
```

